 down january   solstice arena – shut down august   board gamesedit in  zynga in conjunction with hasbro released several physical board games based on the various properties in the zynga game library these games were released under an imprint of hasbro called hasbro gaming as of  the list of available games includes board game versions of draw something and words with friends a cityville edition of monopoly and several kids animal games based on farmville zyngaorgedit main article zyngaorg in  zynga started a nonprofit organization zyngaorg in charge of incorporating charitable contributions into its games such as farmville to date zyngaorg efforts have raised  million for international humanitarian relief efforts and philanthropic initiatives see alsoedit san francisco bay area portal companies portal notesedit referencesedit  a b zynga fact sheet companyzyngacom archived from the original on  retrieved    a b c d e f zynga inc form k securities and exchange commission february    zynga games mau statistacom june    a b takahashi dean december   how zynga grew from gaming outcast to  billion social game powerhouse venturebeat retrieved december     about zynga companyzyngacom zynga retrieved  july    zynga offering sneak peek at nextgen games abc  a b c shambora jessica december   zynga suddenly is everywhere what gives fortune retrieved april   zynga is named after pincuss deceased american bulldog zinga   oneill nick  june  zynga launches farmville does it look familiar allfacebook retrieved  january    lien tracey  september  farmville  represents the next generation of social games says zynga polygon retrieved  january    zynga developer metrics appdata retrieved  january    thompson mike the top  facebook games of january  appdata inside social games retrieved  january    a b facebook and zynga to end close relationship bbc news bbc  retrieved  december    a b zynga ipo goes splatville what went wrong forbes  why zynga is shedding users readwriteweb june     