s charity sister company zyngaorg incorporates charitable contributions into its games the it department for zynga inc is largely based in the companys san francisco ca headquarters though the company also operates a data center in ashburn va with some staff onsite the company has several chief technology officers overseeing productrelated technology the company has recently focused on developing a private cloud in order to reduce its reliance on amazons public cloud services while the company does not intend to cease usage of amazons cloud entirely zynga has shifted approximately  percent of it operations to the companys private cloud the private cloud runs on xenserver and uses cloudstack software there are several other top technology executives leading large groups within the department the enterprise it security group handles cloud computing risk management and strategies the network operations division is responsible for infrastructure data centers software testing vendor selection and procurement small teams within the department handle other functions including oracle applications the microsoft exchange server enterprise systems and the help desk zynga does not have a listed main phone line for external communications and email is the best way to contact its staff the phone number provided in the profile reaches the zynga billing support group sector industry services media employees  revenue m fye  breaking news on investment signals date type inside scoop  staffing topic software staffing company zynga inc san francisco ca opportunity seeking a senior software engineer client austin tx   staffing topic finance staffing company zynga inc san francisco ca opportunity seeking a motion graphic designer  contract san francisco ca   staffing topic staffing company zynga inc san francisco ca opportunity seeking a game programmer  new ip england oxford ox want full access to this profile and more rainkings clients have access to over  new investment signals publis