le charms formerly fairy tale twist  shut down april   roller coaster kingdom – shut down june   ruby blast – shut down january   riches of olympus – shut down april   special forces – shut down august   street racing – shut down in december  skateboard slam –shut down april   the friend game – shut down in february  the pioneer trail formerly frontierville – shut down april   the ville – shut down june   treasure isle – shut down december   vampire wars – shut down december   war of the fallen  shut down august   warstorm – shut down in september  word scramble challenge – pulled from app stores yoville – sold may   zynga bingo  shut down december  zynga slingo – shut down august   zynga plus casino – shut down march  zynga plus poker – shut down march  zynga slots – shut down november   zynga elite slots – shut down april   zombie smash – shut down january   solstice arena – shut down august   board gamesedit in  zynga in conjunction with hasbro released several physical board games based on the various properties in the zynga game library these games were released under an imprint of hasbro called hasbro gaming as of  the list of available games includes board game versions of draw something and words with friends a cityville edition of monopoly and several kids animal games based on farmville zyngaorgedit main article zyngaorg in  zynga started a nonprofit organization zyngaorg in charge of incorporating charitable contributions into its games such as farmville to date zyngaorg efforts have raised  million for international humanitarian relief efforts and philanthropic initiatives see alsoedit san francisco bay area portal companies portal notesedit referencesedit  a b zynga fact sheet companyzyngacom archived from the original on  retrieved    a b c d e f zynga inc form k securities and exchange commission february    zynga games mau statistacom june    a b takahashi dean december   how zynga grew from gaming outcast to  billion social game powerhouse venturebe